name: Elden Ring Ranni The Witch
description:
I add many trigger words in the descriptions.

But actually, the main trigger word is Ranni The Witch, and other words are used to describe her clothes.

Weight: 0.6~1.0

I test this lora on several base models and it works well, except you need add some tags for certain base models.

I trained this lora on AnyLora CKPT.

I'm not sure it is the best choice, but so far it looks good.

I also try ACertain.
